Right, check! Left, check!
Front, check! All okay, mo!

rows.label: tlk42360112_01_msg0002
rows.name:
I'm checking every nook
and cranny of Goldmund for
any abnormalities, mo!

rows.label: tlk42360112_01_msg0003
rows.name:
I won't overlook even the slightest
change, and if there's anything,
I'll repair it immediately!

rows.label: tlk42360112_01_msg0004
rows.name:
We repair crew members are entrusted
with the lives of everyone on Goldmund,
so we can't do a half-hearted job, mo!
